01:17:18.512 --> 01:17:21.162
presentation is also mediated by CHILL.

1277
01:17:21.592 --> 01:17:24.732
And again, it's through causing vascular

1278
01:17:25.112 --> 01:17:28.692
permeability. It looks like CHILL actually is very

1279
01:17:28.732 --> 01:17:32.612
important in causing vascular permeability and thereby

1280
01:17:32.692 --> 01:17:33.312
allowing

1281
01:17:34.292 --> 01:17:37.752
essentially an exit point for

1282
01:17:38.112 --> 01:17:41.772
