1366
01:22:31.216 --> 01:22:33.836
prostate into invasive cancer states.

1367
01:22:34.256 --> 01:22:38.136
So might this mechanism be occurring much earlier during the course

1368
01:22:38.176 --> 01:22:39.506
of tumor evolution-

1369
01:22:39.916 --> 01:22:40.136
Right

1370
01:22:40.146 --> 01:22:41.216
... than metastatic?

